# cellpy workspace — plan documents

The **`architecture-plan`** repository (`../architecture-plan/` from this checkout) is
the **authoritative home for cellpy 2 plan documents** (gap analysis, Stage 0 plans,
loader/config/unit migration plans, etc.).

**Do not use `code-reviews/`** for these plans — that location is obsolete.

When issues or older text reference `code-reviews/cellpy2-*.md`, open the same filename
under `../architecture-plan/` instead.

